---
---
<section class="bg-gray-50 py-20 border-y border-gray-200">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-5xl">

    <div class="text-center mb-14">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">
        The revenue you're already losing
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Most businesses don't have a traffic problem. They have a conversion and follow-up problem.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-8">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-red-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Your website doesn't convert</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Visitors land, look around, and leave. Slow load times and unclear offers quietly bleed every dollar you spend driving traffic.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-8">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-amber-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-amber-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Ad spend leaks into clicks you can't track</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Without a tracked number and clean reporting, you're guessing which dollars actually turned into customers.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-8">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-blue-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Missed calls go unanswered</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          A missed call from a paid lead is a refund on your ad spend. No second chances, no follow-up, gone to a competitor.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>
